
        ------------------------------- Game file Framework -------------------------------
Document
    -> data
        -> maps: Game levels
        -> players: Mario's jason documents

    ///-------> The game components <-------///
    -> element:
        ---> pro_box.py
            The game item box (the one marked by the ? mark) and related actions
        ---> brick.py
            Bricks can be jacked up and broken
        ---> coin.py
            Collect and drop
        ---> enemy.py
            Multiple types of enemies and relative actions
        ---> player.py
            Mario's action
        ---> strengthen.py
            Power up about magic/colorful mushrooms
        ---> stuff.py
            Tiny stuff (eg.flags)
        ---> info.py
            Info panel (Health,grades,etc.)


    ///-------> Events at different stages of the game <-------///
    -> status
        ---> menu.py
            The main menu at the beginning of the game
        ---> load.py
            The loading interface between levels
        ---> level.py

    ---> Constants.py
        The width and height of the screen and Mario's moves

    ---> setup.py
        The code of game starter

    ---> Sound.py

    ---> Tools.py


Materials
    -> music: The background music
    -> sound: Game Button Sound
    -> picture: Characters(player), props, enemies, backgrounds

Main.py
    The main entry of the program and the game start button




